Come on dubstep fans. You really have to feel me with this. Listen to some old tracks. You'll hear the difference instantly. 

Take this one for example: youpoop SFu2DfPDGeU

Don't forget what dubstep is all about. Don't let it be like hardcore, speedcore that's for people who doesn't feel rhytm.
